VerthashMiner
------------------------------------------
GPU miner for the Verthash algorithm

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.6.3-1
  libOpenCL1-2.3.3-2
  libcurl4-8.14.1-1
  libgcc1-12.4.0-3
  libjansson4-2.13.1-1
  libstdc++6-12.4.0-3
  libtiny_sha3_0-0+git20160921-1bl1
  libtinycthread1-1.2+git20161001-1bl2

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  binutils-2.44-1
  cmake-3.28.3-1
  cygport-0.36.9-1
  gcc-core-12.4.0-3
  gcc-g++-12.4.0-3
  libOpenCL-devel-2.3.3-2
  libcurl-devel-8.14.1-1
  libjansson-devel-2.13.1-1
  libssl-devel-3.0.16-1
  libtiny_sha3-devel-0+git20160921-1bl1
  libtinycthread-devel-1.2+git20161001-1bl2
  ninja-1.12.1-1

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/CryptoGraphics/VerthashMiner

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/CryptoGraphics/VerthashMiner/archive/refs/tags/0.7.2.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack VerthashMiner-0.7.2-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./VerthashMiner-0.7.2-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/VerthashMiner-0.7.2-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/VerthashMiner-0.7.2-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(VerthashMiner)
  /usr/bin/VerthashMiner.exe
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/VerthashMiner.README
  /usr/share/doc/VerthashMiner/LICENSE
  /usr/share/doc/VerthashMiner/README.md

